Privacy Policy for Mighty Fish: Watch Game

Effective Date: 20 January 2025

Thank you for using Mighty Fish: Watch Game ("the App"). Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our Apple Watch game.

1. Information We Collect
When you use the App, we may collect the following types of information:
Personal Information: The App does not require personal information such as your name, email address, or phone number.
Usage Data: We may collect anonymous usage data, such as game progress, in-app purchases, and interactions with the App.
Device Information: The App may collect device-related information such as Apple Watch model, operating system version, and unique device identifiers.
In-App Purchases: If you make purchases within the App, transaction details may be processed by the Apple App Store, and we do not have access to your payment information.

2. How We Use Your Information
We may use the collected information for the following purposes:
To provide and improve the App's gameplay experience.
To process in-app purchases and restore previous transactions.
To analyze user engagement and improve our services.
To provide customer support and respond to inquiries.

3. Data Sharing and Disclosure
We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties. However, we may share aggregated, non-personal data with third-party analytics services to help us understand app performance.

4. Third-Party Services
The App may use third-party services such as analytics tools provided by Apple (e.g., App Store Connect), which may collect data in accordance with their respective privacy policies. We encourage you to review Appleâ€™s privacy policy for more details.

5. Data Security
We implement reasonable security measures to protect your data. However, please be aware that no method of data transmission or storage is 100% secure.

6. Your Choices
You can manage your preferences regarding data collection and in-app purchases through your Apple Watch and iPhone settings. You may also delete the App at any time to stop data collection.

7. Children's Privacy
The App is not intended for children under the age of 4. We do not knowingly collect personal data from children.

8. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected by an updated effective date. We encourage you to review this policy periodically.

9. Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or your data, please contact us through Q&A section.

By using Mighty Fish: Watch Game, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.
